{"tid":858300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 可唔可以黎多次","createTime":"2018-10-11T16:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T06:16:01.000Z","uid":101968,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"72fec965ca3be78e4cd85e672be34373615b1f98","tid":858300,"uid":101968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b-ncuhIuqmg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb-ncuhIuqmg&d=pY0agEH7gCaDRQKpRecKoUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ffb1b836\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b-ncuhIuqmg</a><br />\n<br />\n當時無人估到件事會搞到咁大<br />\n香港人正因為團結 先有四年前雨傘革命<br />\n今日港共完全無視港人 嚴重損港人利益<br />\n<br />\n香港人 唔好睇小自己一分力<br />\n攞翻團火 企出黎 話比世界聽<br />\n香港係香港人話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be0c56c6693011f641333e005d5547633c30764","tid":858300,"uid":101968,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:53:11.000Z","msg":"水能載舟 亦能覆舟<br />\n極權政府並不可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edf86e1b72adfdcc4ffd0fc427236698038097a","tid":858300,"uid":101968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b11221642b799fd7c67979dee130f390c973c22","tid":858300,"uid":33004,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"黎乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次如果唔係689條傻西射學生<br />\n最後唔會咁多人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla